:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.1.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Тиббий жиҳоз тўғрисидаги маълумотлар: қўллаш соҳаси, қисқача тавсифи, турлари ва тиббий жиҳоз ва унинг таркибий қисмларининг қисқача тавсифи, мавжуд ҳолларда тиббий жиҳозлар номенклатураси (GMDN) ва жиҳознинг ягона идентификатори (UDI);</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.2.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Тиббий жиҳоз таркибидаги дори воситалари тўғрисидаги маълумотлар (дори воситасининг таркиби, миқдори, дори воситасининг тиббий жиҳоз билан мутаносиблиги, дори воситасини ишлаб чиқарилган мамлакатда рўйхатдан ўтказилганлиги тўғрисидаги маълумотлар). (*) (**)</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(*) ушбу бандларда санаб ўтилган ҳужжатлар дастурий таъминот учун талаб этилмайди.</span></span></span></p><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(**) ушбу бандларда санаб ўтилган ҳужжатлар «in vitro» ташхис воситалари учун талаб этилмайди.</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.3.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Ишлаб чиқарувчи тўғрисидаги маълумотлар: номи, фаолият тури, юридик манзили, мулкчилик шакли, раҳбарият таркиби, мақоми ва ваколатлари кўрсатилган ҳолда бўлинмалар ва шўъба корхоналар рўйхати.</span></span></span></p><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Ишлаб чиқарувчи мамлакатда ишлаб чиқариш ҳуқуқини берувчи ҳужжат нусхаси (мавжуд ҳолларда).</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.4.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Яратиш ва ишлаб чиқариш маълумотлари: техник чизма, ишлаб чиқариш жараёнлари схемаси, ишлаб чиқаришнинг асосий босқичлари, қадоқлаш, синовлар ўтказиш ва тайёр маҳсулотни эркин муомалага чиқариш тартиби.</span></span></span></p><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Маҳаллий тиббий жиҳоз ишлаб чиқарувчисининг ишлаб чиқариш регламенти. (*)</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(*) ушбу бандларда санаб ўтилган ҳужжатлар дастурий таъминот учун талаб этилмайди.</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.5.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Тиббий жиҳоз мувофиқ бўлиши лозим бўлган стандартлар рўйхати ёки умумий спецификациялар рўйхати (улар тўғрисидаги маълумотлар билан).</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="lin