pMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(*) ушбу бандларда санаб ўтилган ҳужжатлар дастурий таъминот учун талаб этилмайди.</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.13.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Махсус дастурий таъминот ҳақида маълумот (мавжуд ҳолларда): верификация ва валидация натижалари, дастурий таъминотнинг архитектураси ва ҳаёт цикли ҳақидаги маълумотлар, киберхавфсизликни таъминлаш бўйича чоралар (яхлитликни назорат қилиш, киришни бошқариш, маълумотларни ҳимоялаш ва рухсатсиз аралашувнинг олдини олиш), идентификация ва маркировка, ишлаб чиқарувчи синовлари натижалари ҳамда талабларнинг бажарилишига оид кузатув тизими.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.14.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Турғунликни ўрганиш ҳисоботи — яроқлилик муддати бўлган маҳсулотлар учун синов натижалари ва хулосаларининг давлат тилига таржимаси билан. </span></span><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(*)</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(*) ушбу бандларда санаб ўтилган ҳужжатлар дастурий таъминот учун талаб этилмайди.</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.15.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Нохуш ҳолатлар ва муомаладан чиқарилиши ҳисоботи (янги яратилган ва лойиҳалаштирилган тиббий жиҳозлар учун ушбу маълумотлар тақдим этилмайди):</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">тиббий жиҳоз қўлланилиши билан боғлиқ нохуш ҳолатлар рўйхати, қатор нохуш ҳолатлар содир бўлган ҳолларда, хабар қилинган ҳолатлар содир бўлган вақт даври, ҳар бир ҳолатнинг қисқача тавсифи ва ҳар бир хабар турдаги ҳолатларнинг умумий сони, муаммоларни бартараф этиш ва ушбу ҳолатларнинг ҳар бирида ишлаб чиқарувчилар томонидан уларни бартараф этиш юзасидан ишлаб чиқилган мувофиқлаштириш режаси (мавжуд ҳолларда).</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Рўйхатдан ўтказишдан кейинги босқичда тиббий жиҳозларнинг хавфсизлиги ва самарадорлиги тўғрисидаги маълумотларни йиғиб бориш ва таҳлил қилиш режаси.</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">2.16.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Тиббий жиҳознинг умумий биологик талабларига мувофиқлигини исботлаш мақсадида ўтказилган уларнинг биологик таъсирини баҳолаш тадқиқотлари (синовлари) баённомалари. (*) (**)</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" c