ss="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"><span style="line-height:normal"> </span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">6.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Тиббий жиҳознинг фотосурати (маҳсулотнинг ташқи кўриниши, бутловчи, сарфлаш қисмлари ва материаллари акс эттирилган ҳолда) ва каталоглари (*).</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">(*) ушбу бандларда санаб ўтилган ҳужжатлар дастурий таъминот учун талаб этилмайди.</span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">7.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Ишлаб чиқаришни ўрганиш (инспекция) ҳисоботи.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:3%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">8.</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:21%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:justify"><span style="background:white"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Тиббий жиҳоз</span></span><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">да қўлланилган интеллектуал мулк объектларига (товар белгилари ва саноат намуналари) бўлган ҳуқуқларни тасдиқловчи муҳофаза ҳужжати (гувоҳнома, патент ва уларга илова) ёки улардан фойдаланиш тўғрисидаги шартнома ёки </span></span><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">тиббий жиҳоз</span></span><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">нинг савдо номи ҳамда дизайни бўйича интеллектуал мулк соҳасидаги ваколатли органнинг хулосаси.</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:14%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p align="center" class="CxSpMiddle" style="text-align:center"><span style="line-height:normal"><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">+</span></span></span></p></td><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:15%; padding:0cm 4px 0cm 4px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top"><p class="CxSpMiddle"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></a></div><div class="FOOTNOTE"><a id="7861072">Изоҳ.</a></div><div class="FOOTNOTE"><a id="7861074">Ариза берувчи ҳужжатларда айрим маълумотларни асослаган ҳолда киритмаслиги мумкин.</a></div><div class="FOOTNOTE"><a id="7861076">Тиббий жиҳознинг битта рўйхатдан ўтказилганлик гувоҳномасига бир нечта модификациялари киритилиши мумкин.</a></div><div class="FOOTNOTE"><a id="7863949">Рўйхатдан ўтказилганлик гувоҳномасининг амал қилиш муддатини узайтириш учун тақдим этилган аризага Ўзбекистон Республикасидаги клиникаларнинг тиббий жиҳознинг хавфсизлиги ва самарадорлиги тўғрисидаги хулосалари тақдим этилади.</a></div><div class="BY_DEFAULT"><a id="7861099"></a></div><div class="APPL_BANNER_LANDSCAPE_TITLE"><a id="7861101">Тиббий жиҳозларни давлат рўйхатидан ўтказиш тартиби тўғрисидаги <a href="javascript:scrollText(7860249)">низомга</a><br />4-ИЛОВА</a></div><div class="BY_DEFAULT"><a id="7861104"></a></div><div class="BY_DEFAULT"><a id="7861107"><table class="Table" style="width:100.0%; background:white; border-collapse:collapse; border:none" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" style="border-bottom:none; width:38%; padding:.100px .100px .100px 2px; height:19px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:none; border-left:none"><p align="center" style="text-align:center"></p></td><td style="border-bottom:none; width:23%; padding:.100px .100px .100px 2px; height:19px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:none; border-left:none"><p align="center" style="text-align:center"></p></td><td colspan="2" style="border-bottom:none; width:38%; padding:.100px .100px .100px 2px; height:19px; background-color:white; border-top:none; border-right:none; border-left:none"><p align="right" style="text-align:right"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:9.0cm"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span lang="UZ-CYR" style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">НАМУНА</span></span></b></span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="border-bottom:none; width:38%; padding:.100px .100px .100px 2px; h